data.description: Plenty of space, inside and out! This beautiful, two-story home is located in The Ridge. This home is just minutes away from Dana Peak Park where you can enjoy hiking, biking, fishing, picnics, or water sports. This Home features a formal dining, a formal living room, a loft-game room, a sitting area, and so much more. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a double oven, and plenty of room for family and entertaining. Downstairs you have the master suite, complete with a double vanity, jetted tub, and a sitting area for relaxation. .SELLER WILL PROVIDE $20,000 CREDIT AT CLOSING WITH A FULL-PRICE OFFER, FOR BUYER TO USE TOWARDS BUYERS CHOICE Call today to schedule your showing!!!
